      <title>普京警告美国导弹袭击德国将引发新冷战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/ukraine-war-putin-says-could-deploy-weapons-if-us-places-missiles-in-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京表示，如果美国继续在德国部署远程导弹，俄罗斯可以部署中程和短程打击武器并增强其海军能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/ukraine-war-putin-says-could-deploy-weapons-if-us-places-missiles-in-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国警告朝鲜可能在美国大选前进行核试验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/south-korea-warns-north-may-do-nuclear-test-nearing-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国国防部长表示，朝鲜可能考虑在美国总统大选临近时进行核试验，以提高其知名度，因为金正恩推出了能够打击美国及其亚洲盟友的新型弹头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/south-korea-warns-north-may-do-nuclear-test-nearing-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:42:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统佩泽什基安任命穆罕默德·礼萨·阿里夫为副总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/iran-s-pezeshkian-names-mohammad-reza-aref-as-vice-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据伊朗国家电视台报道，伊朗新总统马苏德·佩泽什基安任命改革派政治家穆罕默德·礼萨·阿里夫为第一副总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/iran-s-pezeshkian-names-mohammad-reza-aref-as-vice-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:10:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗哈梅内伊表示愿意改善与西方的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/iran-s-khamenei-signals-openness-to-improving-ties-with-west</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗最高领导人表示，伊朗愿意缓解与西方的外交接触，暗示新总统领导下，伊朗可能会采取更为和解的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/iran-s-khamenei-signals-openness-to-improving-ties-with-west</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:47:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列议会夏季休会，内塔尼亚胡的压力减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/israel-hamas-war-parliamentary-recess-takes-heat-off-netanyahu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会于周日休会三个月，为总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡提供一些国内喘息的机会，因为该国面临着对加沙战争的批评、提前举行选举的呼声以及真主党在戈兰高地发动的造成十几名年轻人死亡的毁灭性袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/israel-hamas-war-parliamentary-recess-takes-heat-off-netanyahu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在第一周就筹集了 2 亿美元以建立战争基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/harris-raises-200-million-in-first-week-to-build-up-war-chest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯自参加 2024 年总统大选以来的一周内筹集了 2 亿美元，凸显了民主党人对其新推定候选人的热情高涨，并有助于抵制共和党的闪电战，唐纳德·特朗普在金钱竞赛中领先。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/harris-raises-200-million-in-first-week-to-build-up-war-chest</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉选举开始投票，可能引发重大转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/venezuelan-election-could-lead-to-seismic-shift-in-politics-or-give-president-maduro-six-more-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拉加斯，委内瑞拉（美联社）——委内瑞拉的投票站已开始，周日人们将进行总统选举投票，选举结果要么会导致政局发生重大变化，要么导致造成世界和平时期最严重经济崩溃的政策再延长六年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/venezuelan-election-could-lead-to-seismic-shift-in-politics-or-give-president-maduro-six-more-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 04:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、日本、韩国希望在美国投票前巩固安全关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/us-japan-south-korea-look-to-cement-security-ties-before-america-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国承诺将全力保卫盟友日本和韩国，并与其签署协议，以在 11 月美国选出下一任总统之前巩固安全合作成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/us-japan-south-korea-look-to-cement-security-ties-before-america-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国财政大臣里夫斯详述“破碎不堪”的英国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/uk-chancellor-reeves-to-detail-a-broke-and-broken-britain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯将在周一的演讲中描绘英国公共财政的严峻形势，她将陷入反对党和本党内部批评者的夹缝之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/uk-chancellor-reeves-to-detail-a-broke-and-broken-britain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戈兰致命空袭可能引发以色列严厉报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/deadly-strike-in-golan-triggers-threat-of-harsh-israeli-payback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列占领的戈兰高地发生火箭弹袭击，造成 12 名儿童死亡，20 多名儿童受伤，这引发了人们对以色列和黎巴嫩真主党武装组织之间战斗急剧升级的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/deadly-strike-in-golan-triggers-threat-of-harsh-israeli-payback</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 19:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
